casebody.data:
No. 108,

Orig.

Nebraska v. Wyoming et al.

Motion of the Special Master for compensation and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $84,772.75 for the period June 1 through December 1, 1999, to be paid as-follows: 34% by Nebraska, 34% by Wyoming, 5% by Colorado, 24% by the United States, and 3% by Basin Electric Power Cooperative. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 527 U. S. 1033.]
